Value Required NAME (\S+)
Value TYPE (L2|L3)
Value VR (\S+)
Value IF_COUNT (\d+)
Value SHARED (Y|N)

Start
  # 跳过表头、分隔线和空行
  ^Total\s+zone\s+count.* -> Next
  ^[-=]+.* -> Next
  ^\s+Name\s+Type\s+VR/Vswitch\s+If-count -> Next
  ^\s*$$ -> Next
  ^\s+${NAME}\s+${TYPE}\s+${VR}\s+${IF_COUNT}(\s+${SHARED})? -> Record